   Liebenzell, Germany on 2019-10-(04-06).

   The CfP for interested participants will end on 2019-06-30.

2019-03-30

   There is now a [51]patch overview tool to have a quick overview of the
   patch status list. This list is generated each day from the [52]sites
   repository. It checks if patches apply cleanly in a normal patching
   manner. Of course it does not check patch combinations.
     * [53]Hacking patches guidelines
     * [54]Tool source-code

   Please keep the patches tidy and maintain or remove them.

