2017-03-28

   [82]surf now uses webkit2 by default. The webkit1 version is kept in
   the [83]surf-webkit1 branch. The "master" branch doesn't exist anymore,
   HEAD is now [84]surf-webkit2, so be sure to rebase your local master
   commits onto surf-webkit1.

